{"word":"H1419 - גָּדֹול - gâdôwl - gaw-dole' - Aloud","slug":"H1419","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גָּדֹול</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gâdôwl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gaw-dole'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Aloud"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05D3;&#x05DC;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05D3;&#x05D5;&#x05DC; - ga&#x0302;do&#x0302;l  ga&#x0302;do&#x0302;l</b> - <i>gaw-dole', gaw-dole'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1431\">H1431</a>; <i>great</i> (in any sense); hence <i>older</i>; also <i>insolent: - </i> + aloud, elder (-est), + exceeding (-ly), + far, (man of) great (man, matter, thing, -er, -ness), high, long, loud, mighty, more, much, noble, proud thing, X sore, (&#x05A4;) very."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1420\">H1420</a>, <a href=\"#/H1431\">H1431</a>, <a href=\"#/H1432\">H1432</a>, <a href=\"#/H1433\">H1433</a>, <a href=\"#/H1434\">H1434</a>, <a href=\"#/H1435\">H1435</a>, <a href=\"#/H1436\">H1436</a>, <a href=\"#/H1437\">H1437</a>, <a href=\"#/H3012\">H3012</a>, <a href=\"#/H4024\">H4024</a>, <a href=\"#/H4026\">H4026</a>, <a href=\"#/H4027\">H4027</a>, <a href=\"#/H4028\">H4028</a>, <a href=\"#/H4029\">H4029</a>"}]}